### Scripts for plotting Figure 1 (a, c and d)


### Bozplots of global and per-window distances and diversity in Ophiostoma lineages.

plotBoxplots.R

requirements:
./data/ame1.ame2_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/nov.ame1_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/nov.ame2_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/ulm.ame1_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/ulm.ame2_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/ulm.nov_circos_Dxy.txt
./data/ame1_circos_tP.txt
./data/ame2_circos_tP.txt
./data/nov_circos_tP.txt
./data/ulm_circos_tP.txt



### Dotplot with standard errors of D-statistic

plot_Dstatistic.R

requirements:
Dstats_results.txt



### Circos plot with PCA in windows and tree weighting

mk_circos.sh

requirements:
config_PCA.conf 				# configuration file with circos plot
ideogram_1.conf 				# configuration file with ideogram
ticks_1.conf    				# configurarion file with ticks
./karyotype/karyotype.Ophnul_H327.txt 		# configuration file with chromosomes
./data/PCA_PC1_ulmi_novsp/*.txt			# PCA results for each strain
./data/TreeTopGenome_BlackTopos_subselect.txt	# Results of tree weighting
./data/genes_MAT.txt				# Position of MAT-1 loci
./data/genes_vic.txt				# Position of vic genes
